<!--HTML for list of active operations Advanced Programming project-->

<!DOCTYPE HTML>

<html><head> <title>Operations</title></head>
			<body style= 'font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 25px 50px 75px 50px'><h1>List of operations</h1>
            <p style='border-left:6px solid red'>&nbsp The output of each operation can be displayed by clicking on the relative button!</p>
            <ol>
            <li><p>get the basic information about the dataset <form action='./column_info'>
                <input type="submit" value="column_info" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>obtain the list of unique sequence IDs available in the dataset <form action='./list_seqids'>
                <input type="submit" value="list_seqids"/>
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>obtain the list of unique type of operations available in the dataset <form action='./list_types'>
                <input type="submit" value="list_types" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>count the number of features provided by the same source <form action='./count_features_in_source'>
                <input type="submit" value="count_features_in_source" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>count the number of entries for each type of operation <form action='./count_entries_4type'>
                <input type="submit" value="count_entries_4type" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>derive a new dataset containing only the information about entire chromosomes<form action='./info_entirechroms'>
                <input type="submit" value="info_entirechroms" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>calculate the fraction of unassembled sequences from source GRCh38 <form action='./fraction_unassembled'>
                <input type="submit" value="fraction_unassembled" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>obtain a new dataset containing only entries from source 'ensembl', 'havana' and 'ensembl_havana'
            <form action='./new_havana'>
                <input type="submit" value="new_havana" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>count the number of entries for each type of operation for the dataset containing containing only entries from source
            'ensembl', 'havana'and 'ensembl_havana'<form action='./count_entries_new_havana'>
                <input type="submit" value="count_entries_new_havana" />
            </form></p></li>
            <li><p>return the gene names from the dataset containing containing only entries from source 'ensembl', 'havana' and 'ensembl_havana'
            <form action='./gene_name'>
                <input type="submit" value="gene_name" />
            </form></p></li>
            </ol>
            <div style="position:relative">
            <p style="position:fixed;bottom:2px;width:100%;font-size:14px;font-color:#696969:;text-align:center; background-color:white; "> Advanced Programming project, Genomics 2022/2023 - Ruggiero Alessia, Vincenzi Francesca, Mascagni Marianna  </p></div>

